<br>
here is a thread that will change from your usual worries about AC efficiency.<br>
<br>
the question today is how str effect damage output ?<br>
<br>
we all know str effect is small.<br>
but what is exact effect is a bit less known. Some argue it only change your max damage, some others argue it change your overall damage allowing each hit more chances to hit harder.<br>
<br>
so I would like to know if someone would be able to parse some tests to have a definitive answer.<br>
<br>
Thank you. <p>Sylviania Delaforet<br>
Wood Elf Ranger of Tunare<br>
